1
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:55,270
How are you going to find a kid that you couldn't even find 18 years ago?

2
00:00:55,270 --> 00:00:59,050
If that kid was still alive, he would be 21 years old, right?

3
00:00:59,050 --> 00:01:02,030
Is there someone you suspect?

4
00:01:07,490 --> 00:01:09,960
I see a child.

5
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:13,870
A crying child in the middle of the fire.

6
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:17,610
I've been scared of fire since I was young. Oppa Si Woo is the same.

7
00:01:17,610 --> 00:01:20,970
Yoon Si Woo is a year younger than you!

8
00:01:20,970 --> 00:01:24,220
There was definitely someone.

9
00:01:24,220 --> 00:01:27,480
I don't know who this person is or this child.

10
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:31,040
There's also a rumor going around that Yoon is alive.

11
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:37,650
It had been a while since I was in such pain but this man appeared and alleviated it

12
00:01:37,650 --> 00:01:40,390
with the same method as you, Headmaster.

13
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,970
What did you just say?

14
00:01:48,970 --> 00:01:51,810
I need to meet Hwang Moo Song.

15
00:01:51,810 --> 00:01:59,010
If Moo Song was there on that day, 18 years ago, he will know the truth.

16
00:01:59,010 --> 00:02:00,680
I understand.

17
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:06,510
Also, please find Sim Bong San.

18
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:11,020
You have to find him.

19
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:19,250
Moorim School.
- Episode 14 -

20
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:25,440
I talked with Sang Man hyung and he told me that, like you, everyone is trying to persuade their parents, so not to worry.

21
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:31,120
They will be back soon. He's surprisingly dependable.

22
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:36,540
It looks like Professor Kim Dae Ho is trying very hard. So don't worry too much.

23
00:02:36,540 --> 00:02:38,010
Are you listening?

24
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:44,830
Yeah. You told me five times not to worry.

25
00:02:44,830 --> 00:02:46,660
Did I?

26
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,880
How is Seon Ah ?

27
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:53,980
She is resilient so she'll be fine soon. How about you?

28
00:02:55,130 --> 00:02:58,100
Sim Soon Deok, are you listening?

29
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:02,070
Yeah. I'm okay.

30
00:03:04,170 --> 00:03:09,400
How great would it be if we could all go back to the school soon?

31
00:03:12,490 --> 00:03:15,330
It's not like I'm in a position to say such things.

32
00:03:15,330 --> 00:03:19,000
Don't say this; explain it well to your father.

33
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:22,490
Then you'll be able to go back to school. That's all that matters.

34
00:03:23,530 --> 00:03:26,980
He loses it when we talk about Moorim School.

35
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:30,440
Maybe the reason why he can' t see

36
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:35,140
is connected to your school.

37
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:38,920
Nothing happened, right?

38
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:42,430
No. Nothing is going on, really.

39
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:45,990
Okay, I'll call you later.

40
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:47,860
Okay.

41
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:08,550
That man and woman were the people
who kidnapped me during the field trip.

42
00:04:08,550 --> 00:04:10,840
- Aren't you mistaken as to what you saw?
- I said I am certain!

43
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,450
Aren't they working for your father's company?

44
00:04:13,450 --> 00:04:16,150
Answer directly!

45
00:04:21,810 --> 00:04:24,130
Mom.

46
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:30,850
Chi Ang? Is your body okay?

47
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:32,760
Yes, Mom.

48
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,250
Are you really okay?

49
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:36,800
I am.

50
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:43,770
Mom... do you believe in Father?

51
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,460
Chi Ang...

52
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:51,330
I know this kind of question is weird.

53
00:04:51,330 --> 00:04:54,400
- Even still—
- He's still your father.

54
00:04:55,650 --> 00:05:01,530
He can be selfish and cold, right? He doesn't know how to say nice things.

55
00:05:01,530 --> 00:05:06,160
But still, the fact that he's your father hasn't changed.

56
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:13,820
You might not know it, but your father,

57
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:20,350
in his own way, sent you there because he loves you. I believe that.

58
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:25,480
You're the successor of the Shanghai Group.

59
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:29,070
Don't ever forget it.

60
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,390
Chi Ang, I'm...

61
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:38,160
Don't worry about me, Mom.

62
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:41,650
I wish you were happy.

63
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:46,710
Your happiness is all I wish for.

64
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:52,810
Are you really going to be okay?

65
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:59,800
Of course. I'm okay.

66
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:11,390
Yoon Si Woo! Yoon Si Woo!

67
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:13,380
Yoon Si Woo! Woo!

68
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:15,960
Woah.

69
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,550
You were surprised, weren't you?

70
00:06:17,550 --> 00:06:20,540
I thought you'd cry. Did you wait long?

71
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:24,070
Do you finally understand the worry we felt when you went up to Moorim Peak?

72
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:28,160
When I got all the texts from everyone telling me to come back, my heart went pitter patter.

73
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:32,540
What do you mean pitter patter? Stop sending so many text messages. Because of you—bing! Bing!

74
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,960
I'm about to go crazy.

75
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,980
Did you settle everything with your parents?

76
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:41,380
Of course. At this age am I one to give up just because my parents dragged me away?

77
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:46,750
Teacher Kim kept on begging my parents to let him take me with him.

78
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:49,930
Thank you all so much for coming back.

79
00:06:49,930 --> 00:06:52,300
We're the ones that came back, so why are you thanking us?

80
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:56,440
Also, in this school there are a lot more people who have more at stake than you.

81
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:58,040
This punk...

82
00:06:58,040 --> 00:07:00,030
Let's go in.

83
00:07:01,910 --> 00:07:05,400
So you're telling me you ran away from you family?

84
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:11,640
I didn't realize I could run so fast. No matter what anyone says, I guess I really am a Moorim student.

85
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,950
I'm in Paris right now.

86
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:17,110
My father thinks that I am doing language study abroad.

87
00:07:17,110 --> 00:07:22,650
Enough of this, just bring out some food. After being on a hunger strike for two days,

88
00:07:22,650 --> 00:07:24,030
I'm starving.

89
00:07:24,030 --> 00:07:26,300
Ta-dah! Eat this.

90
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,560
Woah!

91
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,310
Why is it so noisy? Aigoo.

92
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:30,980
Teacher!

93
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:33,950
- Teacher!
- I missed you!

94
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:36,900
You don't see me? I worried so much.

95
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:38,750
Aigoo.

96
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:44,680
Now that I'm back, it's like I'm meeting my uncle. I'm so moved.

97
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,330
You suffered a lot.

98
00:07:46,330 --> 00:07:48,680
Thanks for coming back.

99
00:07:49,790 --> 00:07:52,390
The students came back?

100
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,020
Yes.

101
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:01,630
It seems that Professor Kim Dae Ho did something unnecessary.

102
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:06,450
Alright. You can leave.

103
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:22,620
Now, shall I start moving things along?

104
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:33,980
I told you that I don't want to eat. Please just leave me alone!

105
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:53,710
Leave. Please.

106
00:08:57,480 --> 00:09:02,600
When I think of it, in this school now,

107
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:08,040
the person whose having a more hellish time than me is you.

108
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:16,380
Truthfully, I find all of this confusing, infuriating, and sad.

109
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:26,750
More than the fact that my father lied to me, for the fact that he left me here,

110
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:29,760
I can't seem to forgive him.

111
00:09:37,690 --> 00:09:40,360
But still, I have no choice but to believe in him,

112
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:45,000
because no matter what others say, he's my father.

113
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:51,150
Today, I'll just open the curtains and leave.

114
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:56,580
Let's proceed one step at a time. Slowly. One by one.

115
00:09:57,870 --> 00:10:05,590
If you think about it again and again, an answer will come out, right?

116
00:10:06,450 --> 00:10:09,280
I'm so sorry towards you.

117
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:15,130
Instead of my dad, I'll be the one apologizing.

118
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:28,200
Immediately, all students and professors

119
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:31,060
are to meet in the assembly hall.

120
00:10:32,180 --> 00:10:36,110
Up until now, Moorim School

121
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:41,330
has been without discipline and validation.

122
00:10:41,330 --> 00:10:45,240
You had way too much freedom.

123
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,900
Who is it?

124
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:49,000
- I wonder.
- During this past Moorim Tournament,

125
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:51,760
even if there were some rough times,

126
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:56,500
we won't be shaken by them.

127
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:02,330
This school no longer belongs to Headmaster Hwang Moo Song.

128
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:08,390
Beginning now, this school will undergo great changes.

129
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:14,580
With the start of the change, we'll introduce new teachers.

130
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:19,840
These are your new professors as of today.

131
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:23,540
If all our professors are staying,

132
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:26,200
why would new teachers come?

133
00:11:28,430 --> 00:11:34,230
From now on, I will be in charge of your martial arts education,

134
00:11:34,230 --> 00:11:36,190
I'm Kim Sook.

135
00:11:36,190 --> 00:11:41,590
Moorim School will no longer be your refuge or your playground.

136
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:45,770
During this Moorim Tournament, no one won and everyone had to give up.

137
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:48,130
It was because of the teaching method.

138
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:53,070
For all this time, Headmaster Hwang was teaching you like this.

139
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:57,420
Therefore, he is no longer at Moorim School.

140
00:11:57,420 --> 00:12:03,170
There is no meaning if you can't defend yourself independently,

141
00:12:03,170 --> 00:12:09,410
in a way befitting the name of Moorim School and as a student of Moorim School.

142
00:12:09,410 --> 00:12:12,470
You all have to become stronger.

143
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:17,060
From now on, during the classes

144
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:22,340
the fittest will be able to survive. And since you are Moorim School's students,

145
00:12:22,340 --> 00:12:27,360
I believe you'll follow me well.

146
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:42,940
Professor Kim Dae Ho and Professor Yoo Di,

147
00:12:42,940 --> 00:12:48,820
just like before, you can be in charge of cooking and sports dance classes.

148
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:52,920
What do you mean, just like before? I have half as many classes now.

149
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:57,420
Also, Professor Daniel, you be in charge of basic martial arts training.

150
00:12:57,420 --> 00:12:58,840
Basic martial arts?

151
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,160
If you look at the class schedule you'll see that,

152
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:06,420
in order to raise the students' levels, we've increased the amount of martial arts training.

153
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:09,840
Besides that, there's barely any change.

154
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,720
Nothing has changed?

155
00:13:12,620 --> 00:13:19,200
So, what does the provision "Only assigned teachers are allowed to enter" mean?

156
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:22,880
The new teacher is in charge of all the Moorim martial arts classes,

157
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:25,580
and then are we not allowed to observe the students?

158
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:30,020
All the teachers had their own roles in martial art classes.

159
00:13:30,020 --> 00:13:35,100
If only one teacher is in charge of the students, it can be dangerous and...

160
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:40,560
The new teachers know nothing about the students.

161
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:43,060
How can we not be involved in this?

162
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:48,400
I cannot comply with a unilateral termination like this.

163
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:50,920
Just like I told you last time

164
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:57,130
if you can't comply with the changes, you can still make a decision.

165
00:13:57,130 --> 00:13:58,510
Pardon?

166
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,690
The headmaster has changed now.

167
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:03,990
A bunch of people want to come here as well.

168
00:14:03,990 --> 00:14:05,400
Teacher Beop Gong!

169
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:08,560
I'm not a teacher, but the headmaster!

170
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:10,330
I might have been a teacher in the past,

171
00:14:10,330 --> 00:14:14,300
but now I'm the headmaster of this school. The headmaster!

172
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:29,120
He can't meet Hwang Moo Song.

173
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:32,280
Find a way to buy some time.

174
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,370
Yes.

175
00:14:33,370 --> 00:14:39,000
Also, it looks like Chae Yoon knows about Sim Bong San. What do we do?

176
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:46,640
From what we've observed Sim Bong San hasn't seen the child in 18 years.

177
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:50,240
We'll let them meet. Nothing will happen anyway.

178
00:14:55,910 --> 00:15:01,650
I know that the child was abandoned in a forest.

179
00:15:01,650 --> 00:15:05,530
Does Hwang Moo Song also know about this?

180
00:15:05,530 --> 00:15:07,850
There's no way he would.

181
00:15:07,850 --> 00:15:12,240
But... is it true that Chae Yoon is still alive?

182
00:15:13,130 --> 00:15:15,870
You're trying to know too much.

183
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:32,010
I've searched in the weapons storage, and in the whole school

184
00:15:32,010 --> 00:15:34,760
I couldn't find the key.

185
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:40,520
It's not in his office nor in the school...

186
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:43,660
Could it be in the dorms?

187
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,320
How is Hwang Seon Ah doing?

188
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:50,810
She's not coming out of her room.

189
00:15:50,810 --> 00:15:52,970
Should I search in this room?

190
00:15:52,970 --> 00:15:58,690
Hwang Moo Song wouldn't put his daughter in such danger.

191
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:07,850
Hwang Moo Song... What are you planning?

192
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:18,500
The new classes are starting tomorrow.

193
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:22,900
It's pretty certain the new teachers are going to be tougher about the grading system.

194
00:16:24,170 --> 00:16:27,090
If you miss more classes, it'll be difficult for you.

195
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:34,790
Soon Deok is not at school right now and I don't know what's crossing Chi Ang's mind.

196
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:36,930
At least you should

197
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:47,650
get up soon.

198
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:54,180
It's enough. I ate enough.

199
00:16:57,060 --> 00:16:58,880
Dad.

200
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:06,840
Is it this hard for you if I go back to Moorim?

201
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:20,060
Perhaps...

202
00:17:20,060 --> 00:17:22,980
The reason why your dad can't see

203
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:27,520
might be connected to your school.

204
00:17:29,330 --> 00:17:32,570
I don't know what happened but,

205
00:17:32,570 --> 00:17:37,440
don't hold it in. Talk to me, please.

206
00:17:38,210 --> 00:17:43,830
If I can't understand my Father, who in this world will understand him?

207
00:17:52,560 --> 00:18:00,020
♬ The countless tears which flowed past me ♬

208
