00:20:20,490 --> 00:20:22,840
Let me ask you one thing.

244
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:30,550
Do you have a plan for Soon Deok?

245
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:35,560
I was going to do everything for her.

246
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:45,270
A warm, and comfortable life. A lifestyle that has nothing lacking nor any concerns.

247
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:48,520
I wanted to give a life like that to Soon Deok.

