Do you have anything else to show her aside from yourself?

249
00:20:57,020 --> 00:21:01,020
From the time I first came here until now,

250
00:21:01,020 --> 00:21:06,870
everything here seemed like a dream,

251
00:21:07,410 --> 00:21:09,380
both meeting you

252
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:14,660
and liking Soon Deok.

253
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:24,600
If I just give up on everything here and return,

254
00:21:27,080 --> 00:21:29,650
it'll all become a dream.

255
00:21:33,290 --> 00:21:35,440
What do you want to say?

256
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:42,200
Aren't you returning to your world eventually as well?

257
00:21:43,670 --> 00:21:46,730
Can Soon Deok be in that world?

258
00:21:46,730 --> 00:21:50,060
Can she live there?

259
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:54,500
Do you really believe

260
00:21:57,650 --> 00:22:01,160
you can make her happy?

261
00:22:15,890 --> 00:22:17,150
Did you come back from somewhere?

262
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:22,890
No, I wanted for your father to regain his energy. I bought some abalone.

263
00:22:22,890 --> 00:22:25,100
It's not directly from the sea of course.

264
00:22:25,100 --> 00:22:27,500
Thank you, Ahjumma.

265
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:32,860
There's no need to thank me, but don't say you are going to return to school. Are you?

266
00:22:32,860 --> 00:22:35,180
We ran out of rice.

267
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:42,210
You suffered a lot because I ran away to school, and it didn't work, right?

268
00:22:42,210 --> 00:22:48,540
What was difficult? Are we living thanks to the rice or something?

269
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:55,560
I am starting my part-time job again. I will be back!

270
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:59,210
What, work right now? Soon Deok!

271
00:23:02,410 --> 00:23:05,740
She's trying to be strong...

272
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:09,610
Chicken Maru

273
00:23:13,220 --> 00:23:15,240
Come look, Ahjumma.

274
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:19,980
Doing it like this makes it crispier and more savory.

275
00:23:21,620 --> 00:23:25,660
How about doing a new menu?

276
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:28,960
Taste it.

277
00:23:32,220 --> 00:23:33,320
It tastes good.

278
00:23:33,320 --> 00:23:36,140
Right? It's totally delicious, right!

279
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:40,800
In order to make up for all those days you missed, you sure are doing everything!

280
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:48,500
I don't know. She went to her part-time job.

281
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:49,670
Part-time job?

282
00:23:49,670 --> 00:23:53,820
Yes. We ran out of rice so she went to her part-time job.

283
00:23:53,820 --> 00:23:55,790
It's just...

284
00:23:57,090 --> 00:23:59,270
Yes, welcome.

285
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:01,550
You look very familiar.

286
00:24:01,550 --> 00:24:03,750
Did Sim Soon Deok not come here?

287
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:07,410
-She just went out for a delivery.
- Where did she go?

288
00:24:15,050 --> 00:24:17,100
I'm back!

289
00:24:17,890 --> 00:24:21,170
What about your friend, did you meet him?

290
00:24:21,170 --> 00:24:22,200
My friend?

291
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:28,320
He was really handsome like a celebrity, but he resembled someone.

292
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:42,520
This might be like a dream there, not for me.

293
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:57,570
It has never been this real. I never wanted someone that much.

294
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:02,040
I was passing by this stationery store and when I entered,

295
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:05,490
you know how they sell all those notebooks, right?

296
00:25:05,490 --> 00:25:07,950
After such a long time, it was so fascinating,

297
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:11,380
and because I haven't seen this kind of notebook in a long time,

298
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:15,320
That's why I... I really just...

299
00:25:30,970 --> 00:25:33,740
Assorted notebooks

300
00:25:36,540 --> 00:25:38,520
Yoon Si Woo!

301
00:25:52,730 --> 00:25:56,590
Hey, we're on the street.

302
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:59,950
What if someone recognizes you?

303
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:08,420
Because that child has already become my world.

304
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:16,350
This seems like a quiet place.

305
00:26:18,540 --> 00:26:24,640
Aren't you dragging me into a dark alley?

306
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:29,930
No, that's not it.

307
00:26:30,850 --> 00:26:33,490
Give them to me, your hands are cold.

308
00:26:52,900 --> 00:26:56,260
I forgot to give you the necklace back.

309
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:59,420
Forget it, keep it.

310
00:27:00,220 --> 00:27:04,480
During those times, you said it protected you.

311
00:27:05,890 --> 00:27:11,220
What protects me now isn't that necklace.

312
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:21,890
♬ Today again I see! I see that look! ♬

313
00:27:21,890 --> 00:27:25,990
♬ You, whom I will only love. ♬

314
00:27:25,990 --> 00:27:27,860
That's better.

315
00:27:29,380 --> 00:27:36,510
I missed you.
♬ The person who is waiting for me far away, ♬

316
00:27:36,510 --> 00:27:41,580
Me too.
♬ You are my love ♬

317
00:27:43,280 --> 00:27:50,460
♬ I am laughing over and over again like a half grown child ♬

318
00:27:50,460 --> 00:27:56,710
♬ just to be only walking together with you. ♬

319
00:27:56,710 --> 00:27:58,290
♬ When I see you ♬

320
00:27:58,290 --> 00:28:03,770
- I longed for you.
- Me too.
♬ If I take your hand ♬

321
00:28:03,770 --> 00:28:10,920
Like a madman.
♬ My day will fly by too quickly♬

322
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:18,790
♬ That love is happiness rather than pain ♬

323
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:25,260
♬  is the love which I have learned. ♬

324
00:28:25,260 --> 00:28:27,960
I heard that Director Wang Hao

325
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:31,460
went back to Shanghai.

326
00:28:33,810 --> 00:28:39,770
You might have had to stop at the semi-finals but you did very well at the Moorim Tournament.

327
00:28:39,770 --> 00:28:42,790
You were very outstanding.

328
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:47,150
Your father must also be proud.

329
00:28:47,150 --> 00:28:51,030
If you have any difficulty, you can tell me at any time,

330
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:58,230
because Wang Chi Ang is a student of mine I especially care for.

331
00:29:03,100 --> 00:29:10,530
That time, at this place, didn't you talk about the key that can obtain Cheon Ui Joo?

332
00:29:10,530 --> 00:29:12,390
Why, yes I did.

333
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:17,810
Just what is the Cheon Ui Joo?

334
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:26,690
Cheon Ui Joo is something that can gather all the powers of this world.

335
00:29:26,690 --> 00:29:31,320
A strong person, a natural force for the person

336
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:36,030
who deserved to have this power.

337
00:29:37,770 --> 00:29:42,320
Your father is a strong man.

338
00:29:43,230 --> 00:29:48,580
Working hard to get something you wish for isn't a bad thing.

339
00:29:49,670 --> 00:29:53,430
The bad thing is when you don't make any effort.

340
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:12,300
How is it? I made a new menu item.

341
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:17,160
Because of this, the owner called me to tell me there was a line for it.

342
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,630
This is really good.

343
00:30:20,630 --> 00:30:22,890
I bought those.

344
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:29,440
At a time like this, you need to eat a lot and get strong.

345
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,910
It's good.

346
00:30:41,660 --> 00:30:47,210
It's worse than I thought. After Professor Beop Gong became headmaster,

347
00:30:47,210 --> 00:30:51,200
he summoned new instructors as though he had been waiting.

348
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:57,300
As to the significance for the school, it's the same as if Shanghai Group had taken over.

349
00:30:57,300 --> 00:31:00,990
How is Chi Ang doing?

350
00:31:00,990 --> 00:31:05,280
I don't really know what he's thinking.

351
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:10,060
If even Chi Ang is affected, that's a big problem.

352
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:21,590
- Why?
- Are you really okay?

353
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:26,780
When I called you earlier, your voice didn't sound good. Are you sure there's nothing going on?

354
00:31:28,230 --> 00:31:32,330
Nothing! There's nothing going on.

355
00:31:34,890 --> 00:31:39,580
I guess a good thing did come out of the barrier being broken. We can have dates outside.

356
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:44,860
Date? How is this a date?

357
00:31:44,860 --> 00:31:48,480
Even if we couldn't go to an amusement park or a movie theater,

358
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:52,230
we should have at least eaten ddeokbokki at an outdoor food stand for this to be considered a date.

359
00:31:52,230 --> 00:31:56,470
This isn't like some kind of rendezvous between spies.

360
00:31:56,470 --> 00:31:58,520
Okay, I get it.

361
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:06,180
Going to the amusement park, the movie theater, and the outdoor food stand.

362
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:11,800
We must do all of that in the future.

363
00:32:13,060 --> 00:32:15,600
Okay, for sure.

364
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:34,270
If even the fact that the headmaster had to leave school,

365
00:32:34,270 --> 00:32:36,000
if everything was planned by your father...

366
00:32:36,020 --> 00:32:38,130
If that is a fact, if everything

367
00:32:38,130 --> 00:32:40,780
was indeed planned by my father, what are you going to do?

368
00:32:40,780 --> 00:32:44,440
Could it be that your father wants the Cheon Ui Joo?

369
00:32:45,190 --> 00:32:47,530
It could be what he wants.

370
00:32:59,840 --> 00:33:03,550
Seon Deok is doing well, right?

371
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:14,160
Wang Chi Ang, what are you planning to do from here on?

372
00:33:15,810 --> 00:33:17,520
I don't know.

373
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:22,770
Your father caused the headmaster to leave, but you don't know?

374
00:33:22,770 --> 00:33:26,190
That's right, I don't know.

375
00:33:26,190 --> 00:33:29,780
I came to this school because of Soon Deok and my mom.

376
00:33:29,780 --> 00:33:32,780
But Soon Deok is only looking at you,

377
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:36,410
and at this rate, even my mom...

378
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:41,520
The things that I want,

379
00:33:44,610 --> 00:33:46,930
how could I not get even one of those things?

380
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:54,530
- Or...
- Or?

381
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:01,700
If I just have the Cheon Ui Joo,

382
00:34:05,390 --> 00:34:08,250
I can get everything I want.

383
00:34:11,430 --> 00:34:14,240
The thing that can give you everything in this world.

384
00:34:16,490 --> 00:34:18,830
That's what the Cheon Ui Joo is.

385
00:34:18,830 --> 00:34:20,970
What are you thinking about right now?

386
00:34:20,970 --> 00:34:25,660
I don't know either. So you tell me.

387
00:34:25,660 --> 00:34:28,620
How do I handle the situation?

388
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:35,110
Even though I am confused now,

389
00:34:36,950 --> 00:34:42,680
I'm certain about one thing. My father who will do anything

390
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:50,490
to get what he wants, I resemble him the most.

391
00:34:55,820 --> 00:34:58,780
Because, without any choice, I am my father's son.

392
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,270
No.

393
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,610
You are different.

394
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:25,620
You, the Wang Chi Ang I have come to know over several months,

395
00:35:27,050 --> 00:35:30,500
are different from your father who, because of his purposes, uses illegal means.

396
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:38,180
You treasure the people who are by your side.

397
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:07,440
I said it before. We want strong humans.

398
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:13,760
Moreover, the way the classes were taught will change.

399
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:19,500
We will make you stronger, so you never give up.

400
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:25,070
You'll fight again and again against foes until only a survivor is left.

401
00:36:25,070 --> 00:36:29,390
You will become tough.

402
00:36:36,490 --> 00:36:45,090
Thus, I will teach you just like the Spartans were taught.

403
00:36:45,090 --> 00:36:49,650
Spartan? Is she saying we will be sparring with real, not blunted, swords?

404
00:36:56,780 --> 00:37:01,120
A fight is the essence of fear.

405
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:06,870
Are you going to make your opponent drop to their knees from fear,

406
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:23,500
or are you going to be filled with terror and you yourself go on your knees?

407
00:37:38,790 --> 00:37:45,220
Up until now you were trained with bare hands and wooden swords.

408
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:49,450
You do not know the true meaning of terror or dread.

409
00:37:49,450 --> 00:37:55,300
From now on, you are really going to fight for your life

410
00:37:55,300 --> 00:38:01,750
so that you know the true meaning of victory.

411
00:38:01,750 --> 00:38:07,880
Now, step forward take a sword.

412
00:38:28,830 --> 00:38:31,220
Why are you in my room?

413
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:38,940
Because I heard you missed a week of studies, I was worried.

414
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:42,100
You're saying you came here yourself, for that reason?

415
00:38:42,100 --> 00:38:47,930
Not because the key to Cheon Ui Joo might be with me?

416
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:56,240
Hwang Moo Song wouldn't leave the key with you.

417
00:38:57,740 --> 00:39:03,720
Also, there's this saying, "The darkest spot is at the base of a lamp."

418
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:07,480
If you're so terribly curious why don't you look for it yourself?

419
00:39:15,130 --> 00:39:17,570
Look... Look!

420
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:21,580
Just how important is this Cheon Ui Joo?

421
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:24,220
Is there even such a thing?

422
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:32,350
If it's not in the school, then that means Hwang Moo Song has it.

423
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:42,510
If you know something, it's best for you to tell me everything

424
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:45,300
before whatever that is happens...

425
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:49,570
Just now, is that a threat?

426
00:39:49,570 --> 00:39:55,050
What the hell is the big deal about it? We were like family. How did you change that much?

427
00:39:55,050 --> 00:40:00,950
All humans change depending on the situation.

428
00:40:02,300 --> 00:40:05,960
That is human nature.

429
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:10,490
Just as I expected, you Seon Ha, have changed.

430
00:40:13,740 --> 00:40:15,090
What did you just say?

431
00:40:15,090 --> 00:40:20,250
You think Hwang Moo Song, the man you believed to be your father,

432
00:40:20,250 --> 00:40:24,630
is actually the enemy who killed your real parents.

433
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:28,820
Isn't that why you hate him so much?

434
00:40:28,820 --> 00:40:32,150
No way! That can't be. Dad—

435
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:35,670
Then, why are you holed up in your room?

436
00:40:36,780 --> 00:40:43,170
Isn't it because there is a part of you that can't believe what he has done?

437
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:57,360
However, that isn't your fault.

438
00:40:57,360 --> 00:41:00,380
The situation just turned out that way.

439
00:41:13,390 --> 00:41:18,980
If everything is returned to its proper place now, everything will be finished.

440
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:23,600
Don't make the situation dangerous or difficult.

441
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:58,190
As I expected, it shows that you are an elite. Good job.

442
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:11,970
What the heck is everyone doing?! Do you not want to learn?!

443
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:18,610
It's too early for these students to use real swords.

444
00:42:19,410 --> 00:42:25,860
The students? Does that include yourself?

445
00:42:25,860 --> 00:42:32,820
I heard that you showed exceptional skills at the Moorim Tournament.

446
00:42:33,580 --> 00:42:37,590
Any of the students here will be able to impale someone with these.

447
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:44,040
But we will not hurt our friends with these.

448
00:42:44,810 --> 00:42:50,500
Friends? I haven't heard such a sweet word in a while.

449
00:42:50,500 --> 00:42:53,290
I don't think so.

450
00:42:54,780 --> 00:43:01,160
This is the last time I'll say it. From now on, during the classes in this school, there won't be such harmless weapons.

451
00:43:01,160 --> 00:43:04,970
Of course, there are no friends here either.

452
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:15,690
Have you managed to obtain the key to the Cheon Ui Joo?

453
00:43:19,510 --> 00:43:23,240
The chairman wants a fast answer.

454
00:43:25,340 --> 00:43:31,230
It is either within the school or Hwang Moo Song has it.

455
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:33,530
It is one of these two possibilities.

456
00:43:33,530 --> 00:43:37,060
So, what are you saying? Which one is it?

457
00:43:37,900 --> 00:43:40,130
Let's not be hasty.

458
00:43:40,130 --> 00:43:43,120
The rats have already gone inside the trap,

459
00:43:43,120 --> 00:43:49,740
and does it matter what color cat is able to catch those rats?

460
00:43:49,740 --> 00:43:54,360
Is there even a way to catch those rats?

461
00:43:55,480 --> 00:44:02,930
Chairman Wang Hao says Chae Yoon is the last card he will play.

462
00:44:02,930 --> 00:44:05,830
Are you saying that we should use Chae Yoon?

463
00:44:05,830 --> 00:44:10,910
Hwang Moo Song and Chae Yoon used to be best friends.

464
00:44:10,910 --> 00:44:18,380
If we use Chae Yoon, we may be able to figure out what Moo Song knows.

465
00:44:18,380 --> 00:44:23,140
For example, the location where the key to Cheon Ui Joo is hidden.

466
00:44:23,140 --> 00:44:28,150
However, right now Chae Yoon is desperately focused on finding the other students.

467
00:44:28,150 --> 00:44:30,270
If he comes here and bumps into the daughter—

468
00:44:30,270 --> 00:44:34,780
We'll kill two birds with one stone then.

469
00:44:34,780 --> 00:44:38,510
For all this time, Hwang Moo Song, with Chae Yoon' s

470
00:44:38,510 --> 00:44:43,650
daughter, has been hiding in this school.

471
00:44:43,650 --> 00:44:48,400
Isn't it a better card hand to make

472
00:44:48,400 --> 00:44:51,980
Chae Yoon suspicious that Hwang Moo Song was a member of the destructive force?

473
00:44:57,500 --> 00:45:04,880
Then, please relay my thoughts to the chairman.

474
00:45:47,400 --> 00:45:49,370
Why is the room in this state?

475
00:45:50,550 --> 00:45:53,950
Did something happen? By chance—

476
00:45:53,950 --> 00:45:56,910
I did it.

477
00:45:58,640 --> 00:45:59,440
You?

478
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:03,330
What the heck is this Cheon Ui Joo that it's got everyone riled up?

479
00:46:03,330 --> 00:46:04,130
Seon Ah...

480
00:46:04,130 --> 00:46:06,610
I don't know what kind of incredible thing it is, but

481
00:46:06,610 --> 00:46:09,730
it's just a terrible hardship and inconvenience to me.

482
00:46:09,730 --> 00:46:14,440
Even more so, at times like this, you have to remain calm and strong.

483
00:46:19,570 --> 00:46:24,590
Honestly, I want to just disappear, but

484
00:46:26,640 --> 00:46:29,990
I have nowhere to go.

485
00:46:40,260 --> 00:46:43,400
Up until recently, it was like that for me too.

486
00:46:44,320 --> 00:46:49,630
But when I had no where to go, no one to lean on,

487
00:46:51,590 --> 00:46:55,460
you told me to come to the Moorim School.

488
00:46:56,910 --> 00:46:58,800
Do you not remember?

489
00:46:59,840 --> 00:47:04,920
That's why this time, I'll tell you.

490
00:47:06,130 --> 00:47:08,740
Stay at Moorim School, Hwang Seon Ah.

491
00:47:10,130 --> 00:47:15,440
Didn't Headmaster say that all problems are inside one's self?

492
00:47:16,560 --> 00:47:22,440
Your solution is definitely inside you.

493
00:47:55,090 --> 00:47:59,010
From Soon Deok's kidnapping to the school's violence,

494
00:47:59,010 --> 00:48:02,180
what is your father's intention?

495
00:48:02,180 --> 00:48:05,320
